{
  //########################################
  // Dialogues for Emily
  //########################################

  "Emily.Dialogue.Introduction": "Ooh!... I can read it on your face. You're going to love it here in Pelican Town.#$b#If you're ever looking for something to do in the evening, stop by the saloon. That's where I work!",

  "Emily.Dialogue.Resort_Entering": "Oh, I like this place! It's full of parrots!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Resort_Leaving": "Ah... my lungs feel perfect.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Resort_Shore": "Can you feel it? The ocean has a profound healing energy.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Resort_Chair": "Are you having fun, @? You need to remember to take breaks now and then too!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Resort_Bar": "It's nice to be on this side of the bar for once!$h",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Resort": "If you open your heart to the sun, you can feel a loving energy inside of you.$h",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Resort_Dance": "%Emily is lost in the music.",

  "Emily.Dialogue.danceRejection": "I'm very sorry... but I've already agreed to dance with someone else.$u",
  "Emily.Dialogue.divorced": "@... You broke my heart... I just can't talk to you anymore.$s#$e#Please, let me try to heal...$s",
  "Emily.Dialogue.dumped_Girls": "...$s",
  "Emily.Dialogue.breakUp": "B...But I thought we had a special bond... *sniff*$s",
  "Emily.Dialogue.reject_866": "Oh, that's beautiful... I have a friend who would love that! But she lives far from here...",
  "Emily.Dialogue.secondChance_Girls": "@... I'm ready to give you a second chance. I still have faith that there's a good person inside of you.$s",

  "Emily.Dialogue.event_dance1": "Thank you!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.event_dance2": "Um... Okay. Sorry you didn't like it. I guess those three years of practice were a complete waste...$s",
  "Emily.Dialogue.event_dance3": "Did you really think so? That's exactly the effect I was shooting for!$h#$b#I'm so glad you liked it.",

  "Emily.Dialogue.Mon": "Have I told you Haley and I are sisters? Strange, isn't it?",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Mon2": "I have a secret hobby, but I won't say any more.#$e#Maybe I'll show you some day.$h",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Mon4": "This world is full of spirits and magic... Some don't believe me, but I know it's true.#$e#I can see it in your eyes... you believe in the other world, like me.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Mon6": "I wish Haley would get a job or at least contribute to cooking and cleaning.$s#$e#I think she's hoping to marry someone rich.$u",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Mon6_inlaw_Haley": "I have to say, now that Haley's gone I've had a much easier time keeping things in order.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Mon8": "There's good people in this town who just can't seem to find happiness. It makes me sad.$u#$e#Working in the saloon, I hear first-hand about everyone's problems.$u",

  "Emily.Dialogue.Tue": "I work part-time at Gus' saloon. It pays the bills.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Tue4": "I'm just working at Gus' to make ends meet... but my real passion is tailoring.$u#$e#I made these clothes from scratch, see?",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Tue6": "Oh, hi... It's nice of you to visit me like this.$h",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Tue8": "You know, @... I think the future looks bright for both of us.",

  "Emily.Dialogue.Wed": "I've heard rumors of rare and powerful magic rings, forged long ago by forgotten civilizations. I'm not sure if it's true or just a fairy tale.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Wed4": "You catch fish? I just hope you treat the poor things humanely.$s#$e#Every critter deserves our respect, even the slimy ones.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Wed6": "Have faith... every day you're taking one more step on the path of your destiny.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Wed8": "Hi, @.$u#$e#I always knew we'd become close like this...",

  "Emily.Dialogue.Thu": "I hope you're farming in a sustainable way. The valley's ecosystem is fragile!#$e#How do I know? I have a strong gut-feeling!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Thu4": "Sometimes the flowers speak to me... each one has a different story to tell!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Fri": "Ah, spring. The season of pastels. I actually prefer jewel tones, myself.#$b#Oh, excuse me! I was mumbling about fashion again, wasn't I?",

  "Emily.Dialogue.Sat": "I like making my own clothes, but it's not easy to get cloth.#$e#And it's such a long trip to the city.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Sat6": "Do you ever think about the texture of fabric, @? Each texture has a distinct personality... feel my dress... see?",

  "Emily.Dialogue.Sun": "Hi @!#$e#Do you raise sheep in your barn? You can turn their wool into beautiful bolts of cloth!#$e#You'll need a loom, though. You can make them yourself if you know the crafting recipe.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.Sun4": "This house was left in our care by my parents. They've been traveling the world for the last two years.#$e#We have no idea when they'll be back.#$e#I enjoy living here, though. It's a beautiful area and the town is nice.",

  //--------------

  "Emily.Dialogue.summer_Mon": "Haley is a picky eater. It's so hard to cook for her.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.summer_Mon4": "Eating healthy is very important to me. I want to live a long and active life.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.summer_Mon_inlaw_Haley": "Haley and I get along much better now that she's moved out. I look forward to her visits!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.summer_Tue": "Hello there, @.#$e#I feel lazy today.$u",
  "Emily.Dialogue.summer_Tue6": "I feel bad for Linus. People judge him, but he's just living a different lifestyle.$u#$e#I wish everyone could learn to be accepting of others.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.summer_Wed": "It doesn't rain much in summer, does it?#$e#That just means more watering work for you, huh?#$e#Or do you enjoy the sunny weather?",
  "Emily.Dialogue.summer_Thu": "I consider the bees and butterflies to be my special friends!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.summer_Fri": "If I wasn't so busy I'd come help you on the farm!#$e#But Gus would be upset if I had another job...$s",
  "Emily.Dialogue.summer_Fri6": "You know, I'm sure Gus would understand if I wanted to leave the Saloon someday.#$b#There's so much out there, I can't stay a barmaid forever.$u",
  "Emily.Dialogue.summer_Sat": "Don't overwork yourself or you might end up in Harvey's clinic!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.summer_Sun": "Hi @!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.summer_Sun4": "It's around this time of year that my good friends visit the region... I mean the parrots!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.summer_Sun6": "Hi, @! We've become decent friends, haven't we?$h#$e#That's fine with me. You're a cool guy.^I'm glad.$h",
  "Emily.Dialogue.summer_Sun8": "Hi, @! We've become decent friends, haven't we?$h#$e#This may sound weird, but I've always been certain this would happen.",

  //--------------

  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_1": "Well, fall is here. Time to plant some new crops, huh?",
  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_Mon": "It's good weather for a picnic, isn't it?",
  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_Mon8": "If I didn't have to work I'd suggest we go on a nice picnic!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_Tue": "Hello. Did you have a good summer?",
  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_Tue4": "Hi @! I bet your farm did great this past summer, huh?#$e#You're an excellent farmer.$h",
  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_Wed": "My friend runs a shop in the desert. If you ever go there stop in and say hi for me.#$e#I think she sells some rare products.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_Thu": "Are you friends with Clint? He's a nice guy, if you get to know him.#$e#He gets lonely working in his shop all day. But he's so shy he has trouble making new friends.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_Thu8": "I think Clint's mad at me. He never looks at me anymore...$u#$e#I always thought we were friends.$u",
  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_Fri": "Another beautiful fall day.#$e#It's a pity it'll soon be over.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_Fri6": "Smell that clean air? It's lovely, isn't it?#$b#I just fear that the Joja Co.'s of the world will take this away from us.$u",
  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_Sat": "Keep your mind open and some interesting things might take root.#$e#Anyway, how is your day going?",
  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_Sat6": "I don't have any huge plans for life. I prefer not to stress about the future.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_Sun": "Nothing like a sunny sunday to lift the spirits!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_Sun6": "There's so many invisible barriers holding us back. Why can't people learn to let go and celebrate freedom?#$e#Me? Well, you know what they say... 'You can't cage a wild Junimo'.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.fall_Sun10": "You're such a nice person, @! Thanks for being my friend.$h",

  //--------------

  "Emily.Dialogue.winter_Mon": "Be careful an icicle doesn't fall on your head!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.winter_Mon10": "Be careful an icicle doesn't fall on your head! I wouldn't want you to get hurt!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.winter_Tue": "Oh, hello @!$h#$e#You must be getting very good at farming by now, huh?",
  "Emily.Dialogue.winter_Tue2": "I bet you're an excellent farmer by now!",
  "Emily.Dialogue.winter_Tue4": "I think my hair is frozen solid...$s",
  "Emily.Dialogue.winter_Wed": "Haley and I aren't made for such a big house. It's a hassle to keep it clean.#$e#Ah well. I really shouldn't be complaining.#$e#Your farmhouse seems nice and cozy.$h",
  "Emily.Dialogue.winter_Thu": "It must be so cold for the poor fish.$s#$e#I wonder if any fish hibernate? Maybe I should ask Demetrius.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.winter_Fri": "If I wasn't so busy I'd help you dig around in that cave by the lake.#$e#I bet there are some powerful crystals inside there.",
  "Emily.Dialogue.winter_Sat": "Do you know how to cook 'Bean Hotpot'?#$e#I like that dish quite a bit.$h%revealtasteEmily207#$e#It's hard to get fresh ingredients in the winter, huh?",
  "Emily.Dialogue.winter_Sun": "Hi!#$e#...Yes?",
  "Emily.Dialogue.winter_Sun6": "My sister and I might fight sometimes, but I would really miss her if she left.#$e#I think she'll become a very nice young lady some day... Don't tell her I said that.$h#$e#So, is there anything you want to talk about?",
  "Emily.Dialogue.winter_Sun6_inlaw_Haley": "Say hi to my sister for me! And remind her to visit me tomorrow.",

  //########################################
  // Dialogues for Emily Marriage
  //########################################

  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Indoor_Day_0": "Another beautiful day on %farm farm... I have faith that something good will happen today!$h",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Indoor_Day_1": "Here, take this. It's for you.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Indoor_Day_2": "Hey, someone must've gotten a good night of sleep... you look fresh this morning.$h",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Indoor_Day_3": "My horoscope for the day isn't too good... but I'm going to make the best of it, as always. Let's get to work!",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Indoor_Day_4": "Ughh... *gurgle*... I ate too many bran muffins for breakfast.$s",

  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Indoor_Night_0": "Is that a new hole I see in your shirt? I can sew that up for you, no problem.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Indoor_Night_1": "Welcome home, @. I hope you had a wonderful day.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Indoor_Night_2": "Is it bed time already? My, the day just floated away from me again.$u",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Indoor_Night_3": "Ah, that aroma! It can only be you.$h#$e#It's a good smell.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Indoor_Night_4": "I swept the whole house, washed the windows, dusted, and cleaned the fridge. It was a very productive day!",

  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Rainy_Day_0": "I wonder where the flying insects go when it rains? Don't they get hit by the raindrops?",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Rainy_Day_1": "A day like this is a blessing from mother nature.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Rainy_Day_2": "Good morning... I got this gift for you. Don't worry, I already purified it with sage incense.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Rainy_Day_3": "I meant to let the parrot go free, but his wing never fully healed. He seems content, though. I give him lots of attention.#$e#He told me that he's happy here.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Rainy_Day_4": "I never told you this... but when you first moved here I had a dream about you. I knew right then that our life-paths would intertwine.$4",

  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Rainy_Night_0": "Every moment has a unique and precious beauty... do you notice? It can be easy to forget, sometimes.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Rainy_Night_1": "I can hear the plants talking to each other... they're so happy after today's rain!",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Rainy_Night_2": "How was your day, @? You look a little soggy.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Rainy_Night_3": "My day was very peaceful. How was yours?",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Rainy_Night_4": "Want some dessert? It's my special raw, gluten-free version, sweetened only with cactus syrup.$h",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Rainy_Night_5": "Does the sound of rain ever put you in a trance?",

  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.patio_Emily": "This is my favorite spot for a morning meditation.#$e#I visualize the energy from this crystal garden flowing through my body.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.spouseRoom_Emily": "I'm going to spend some time with the parrot today. It breaks my heart that he'll never fly again.$u",

  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Outdoor_0": "I love getting up early. There's a certain freshness to the air and the wildlife is much more active.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Outdoor_1": "What's on the agenda today, dear?",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Outdoor_2": "Oooh! Ooh! I saw another one!$h#$e#I'm counting squirrels.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Outdoor_3": "A little sunlight is good for you. Just don't get crispy, okay?",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Outdoor_4": "Good morning! I was wondering when you'd finally roll out of bed!$h#$e#It's okay, @... you deserve a good night of rest.",

  "funLeave_Emily": "I'm going to visit town today, and later on I'm going to help out at the saloon. Have a nice day.",
  "funReturn_Emily": "My day went well... it's good to get out of the house now and then.",

  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.OneKid_0": "I hope we can raise %kid1 to be kind and considerate. That's more important than getting A's in school.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.OneKid_1": "Is one child enough, or should we raise another?#$e#I guess we'll just see where fate leads us.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.OneKid_3": "I lit a pale green candle and shook a sprig of baby-mint over %kid1. That should ward off any dangerous spirits.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.TwoKids_1": "A big house, two kids and a parrot... I have my hands full!",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.TwoKids_2": "Well, %kid2 certainly has your hair...$u",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.TwoKids_3": "Oh, I already fed the kids their organic quinoa puffs with goat milk. You just focus on the farm!",

  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Good_1": "This is so fun to live together! I always thought I'd be single my whole life.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Good_2": "It was our destiny to be together... I believe that with all my heart!",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Good_3": "Thanks for taking me into your home. I love this new life.$4",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Good_4": "Our vibrational energies are perfectly in tune. Can't you feel it?",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Good_5": "I was just admiring my wedding amulet... The shell is beautiful! I can feel the pure blue energy radiating from it.$l",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.Good_6": "I had another dream about us last night. We had climbed to the top of a crystal tree, looking down on the most lush and beautiful meadow. I keep having this dream.#$e#I don't know what it means, but I feel that it's a good omen.",

  "Neutral_0": "I hope you'll still like me when I grow old and my hair turns to a dull, faded steel.",
  "Neutral_8": "I feel uninspired today.$s",


  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.spring_1": "Happy new year, honey. Let's make this a special one.$4",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.spring_2": "My friends, the plants, have come back to life. I feel content.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.spring_22": "Hmm... I'm thinking maybe a salad of fresh foraged greens for dinner tonight?",

  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.summer_2": "May Yoba bless you on this lovely day.$7",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.summer_20": "The energy in our bodies fluctuate just as the seasons do. Understanding your own unique rhythym is the first step to inner harmony.",

  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.fall_1": "The year's already half-way over. Can you believe it?",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.fall_25": "Our bodies are naturally in tune with the seasons. This light and color of fall compels us to prepare for the barren winter.#$e#To our distant ancestors, this feeling was encompassing and vital. For us, it only barely peeks through the noise of modern life.",

  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.winter_2": "I can't help but think of all the poor, frozen squirrels out there right now.$s",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.winter_5": "*sigh*... Why does there have to be war and hatred in the world?$s",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.winter_15": "On a day like this, I have a craving for cinnamon, nutmeg, clove, and cardamom.",

  //5% chance each day.

  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.spring_Emily": "I'm feeling excited for a new year of farming, @!$h",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.fall_Emily": "I drank a super-food smoothie this morning and I feel aaah-mazing!$h",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.summer_Emily": "Phew! It's hot but it feels great, doesn't it?#$e#Maybe we'll see some wild parrots today.",
  "Emily.Dialogue_Marriage.winter_Emily": "Whoops, my hair is frozen solid again.$s",


